 ||''[[Annie Ki Ayegi Baraat]]''|| Saima Chaudry ||<ref name=tvwork1/>\n|-\n| 2012 ||''[[Meray Dard Ko Jo Zuban Miley]]''|| Zakia || Also a writer\n|-\n|2013\n|''[[Kabhi Kabhi (2013 TV series)|Kabhi Kabhi]]''\n|Aarez's mother\n|\n|-\n| 2013 ||''Bushra Bara Boor''|| Bushra || \n|-\n|2013\n|''[[1st Hum Awards]]''\n|Presenter\n|\n|-\n| 2013\u20132014 ||''[[Pakistan Idol (season 1)]]''|| Judge ||<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.dawn.com/news/1061277 |title=Idol worship |last=Syed |first=Madeeha |date=8 December 2013 |website=Dawn|location=Pakistan  |access-date=26 March 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2014 ||''[[Jab We Wed]]''|| Faris's Mother ||<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.desiblitz.com/content/most-beautiful-pakistani-tv-actresses |title=20 Most Beautiful Pakistani TV Actresses |date=13 January 2019 |website=DESIblitz  |access-date=26 March 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2015 ||''[[Tum Mere Paas Raho]]''|| Tabish's Mother || \n|-\n| 2015 ||''Utho Geo Pakistan''|| Host ||<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://blogs.tribune.com.pk/story/31177/10-things-morning-shows-did-in-2015-that-we-dont-want-in-2016/ |title=10 things Morning Shows did in 2015 that we don't want in 2016  |access-date=26 March 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n|2015\n|''[[Khuda Dekh Raha Hai]]''\n|\n|<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://tribune.com.pk/story/853244/11-pakistani-dramas-you-cant-miss-this-year/ |title=11 Pakistani dramas you can't miss this year! |date=18 March 2015 |website=The Express Tribune  |access-date=26 March 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n|2015\n|''Dil Hai Chota Sa''\n|\n|<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://blogs.tribune.com.pk/story/65715/pakistani-dramas-are-romanticising-rape-and-brothels-but-saying-the-word-talaaq-is-the-real-problem/ |title=Pakistani dramas are romanticising rape and brothels but saying the word \"talaaq\" is the real problem?  |access-date=26 March 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2015\u20132016 ||''Riffat Aapa Ki Bahuein''|| Riffat Aapa || \n|-\n| 2016 ||''[[Udaari]]''|| Sheedan ||[[Hum Award for Most Impactful Character]]<ref>{{Cite web |u